?frequency

fredr_request(
  endpoint = "series/observations",
  series_id = "A191RL1Q225SBEA",
  observation_start = "1990-01-01",
  observation_end = "9999-01-01",
  frequency = "q",
  units = "lin") %>%
  mutate(value = as.numeric(value))%>%
  mutate(date = ymd(date))%>%
 ggplot(mapping = aes( x = date, y = value)) + geom_line( color = "deeppink4", size = 1) +
  geom_jitter( size = 3.75, color = "ivory", alpha = .25) +
  labs(title = "Percent change in Real GDP", subtitle = "From January 1990 to present", caption = "Source: Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis" )  +
  labs( x= "Date", y = "Percent Change") +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, size = .1, color = "black", alpha = 1)+
  theme_test(base_size = 40)
